Interface BinarySearchTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BinaryTree<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultBinarySearchTree

    public interface BinarySearchTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends BinaryTree<T>
    BinarySearchTree is the interface for a basic binary search tree. The binary search tree contains Comparable objects as data with the invariant that all data in the left subtree of a node is less than the data at the node, and all data in the right subtree is greater than or equal to the data at the node.
